            </svg>
            <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0 mx-3">Book Recommender</h3>
          </a>
  
          <ul class="nav col-12 col-lg-auto me-lg-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0">
            <li><a href="/" class="nav-link px-2 text-secondary">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">FAQs</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">About</a></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="text-end" id="authButtons">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2"><a href="/login">Log in</a></button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-light color-c4"><a href="/register">Sign-up</a></button>
          </div>
          <div class="text-end d-none" id="userInfo">
            <span class="text-white me-3" id="userName"></span>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light" id="logoutBtn">Logout</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container col-xxl-10 px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
        <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
          <img src="./images/objects.jpg" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Bootstrap Themes" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">Your personal literary guide</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Online book recommender. Explore our catalog and find your next read.
            Try now!
          </p>
          <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2" id="btnone">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-search-heart me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                <path d="M6.5 4.482c1.664-1.673 5.825 1.254 0 5.018-5.825-3.764-1.664-6.69 0-5.018"/>
                <path d="M13 6.5a6.47 6.47 0 0 1-1.258 3.844q.06.044.115.098l3.85 3.85a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 1.415l-3.85-3.85a1 1 0 0 1-.1-.115h.002A6.5 6.5 0 1 1 13 6.5M6.5 12a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0-11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0 11"/>
              </svg>
              <a href="/login">Explore</a>
              </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4" id="btntwo"><a href="/register">Sign-up</a></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container px-4 py-5 col-xxl-10" id="hanging-icons">
      <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Why we? What you find with us?</h2>
      <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
          <div class="text-body-emphasis d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.4em" height="1.4em" fill="var(--c2)" class="bi bi-star-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
              <path d="M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Personalized Recommendations</h3>
            <p>A book recommendation app can analyze your preferences, reading history, and favorite genres to suggest books that align with your tastes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
          <div class="icon-square text-body-emphasis d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.4em" height="1.4em" fill="var(--c2)" class="bi bi-calendar-check-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
              <path d="M4 .5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0V1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v1h16V3a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1V.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0V1H4zM16 14V5H0v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2m-5.146-5.146-3 3a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-1.5-1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708L7.5 10.793l2.646-2.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Builds a Reading Habit</h3>
            <p>Enjoying what you read encourages you to make reading a regular part of your life, which can lead to a lifetime of learning and discovery.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
          <div class="icon-square text-body-emphasis d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.4em" height="1.4em" fill="var(--c2)" class="bi bi-clock-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
              <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0M8 3.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0V9a.5.5 0 0 0 .252.434l3.5 2a.5.5 0 0 0 .496-.868L8 8.71z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Saves Time</h3>
            <p>Instead of spending hours browsing bookstores or reviews, an app provides curated suggestions instantly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center my-5">
      <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide col-8">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" class=""></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" class="active" aria-current="true"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="./images/objects.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="family">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="./images/open-book-pages.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="dog">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="./images/Terracotta Sage Green Bookshelf Zoom Virtual Background.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="couple">
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

